{"pageProps":{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji19","name":"毛泽东全集第19卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/maoquanji19.pdf"],"article":{"title":"在延安中央党校的讲话","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"在延安中央党校的讲话"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1944年11月）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的同志脑袋像个西瓜一样，西瓜表面是绿的，很纯净没有什么，但是切开一看，都是旁的颜色，红黑籽，啥都有。有人表面看挺好，脑袋里装着自私自利，有封建迷信·..这些复杂的观念是我们的包袱，就是敌人。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1944,"month":11}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":214,"page_end":214},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"发言"}]}]},"__N_SSG":true}